body.description: Marvel Spidey and His Amazing Friends Electronic Suit Up Spidey action figure is a super hero toy kids won't want to put down! This large scale 10-inch Spidey toy is easy to hold during playtime, to stand up for display, or as a Marvel hero buddy to watch Disney Junior's Spidey and His Amazing Friends with! Electronic Suit Up Spidey features a mask kids can flip up and down to reveal Peter Parker's face, sounds and phrases from the show, and an icon on Spidey's chest that lights up. This Spidey and Friends toy also includes 2 web projectile accessories kids can blast from one of Spidey's wrists for even more imaginative interaction during playtime. Spidey's other wrist also has an attached web accessory with a spinning feature! Imagine defeating baddies by setting up the included standing Green Goblin target for web blasting fun! Marvel's Spidey and His Amazing Friends toys make great gifts for boys and girls ages 3 and up, and for any occasion. (Each sold separately. Subject to availability.) Copyright 2023 MARVEL. manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Marvel Spidey and His Amazing Friends | Electronic Suit Up Spidey Interact With Spidey! Marvel Spidey and His Amazing Friends Electronic Suit Up Spidey is a 10-inch-scale interactive toy figure with lights and sounds that little Spidey fans will love having as their new friend!

Product Features: Peter Parker's Suited Up! He's suited up and ready for action and fun with Team Spidey and all his preschool friends! Kids can pretend to complete Spidey's suit transformation by flipping his mask up and down. Web-Spinning Fun! Another web accessory is already attached to Spidey's other wrist and has an awesome spinning feature! Blast the Baddies! Help Spidey defeat the baddies! Insert included web projectiles in one wrist and press button to launch at Green Goblin!
